name: Metropolitan-Suite--Metropolitan-Kitchenette---View-from-Sleeper-Sofa
caption: Metropolitan Kitchenette - View from Sleeper Sofa
description: This kitchenette includes a dishwasher, fridge, and a sink.
alt: Just to the right of the wall you will find a sink. To the right of the sink a dishwasher built into the cabinets. Above the cabinets, you will see additional mirrored cabinets of which a microwave is contained. In front of the kitchenette, a table and lamp sit just to the right of the sleeper sofa.
